Create Another Class Extending Fragment Class
	-	override onCreateView() method
	-	use inflater to inflate the layout from the resources
			
			inflater.inflate(R.layout.fragment_main, container, false);
			
In Main Activity Layout
	-	Add FrameLayout to MainLayout
	-	create object of created Fragment
			
        	firstFragement firstFrag = new firstFragement();
        	
    -	 add object of Fragment to FrameLayout created in the Main Activity Layout
    		getFragmentManager().beginTransaction().add(R.id.fragment1, firstFrag).commit(); 